data.description: Come and See this very  nice end unit, 2BR condo in Lower Allen Township, convenient to Rt. 15, Shiremanstown and shopping! Both bedrooms are very nice sized and have great closet space! Living room is enhanced by wood laminate flooring and natural light. This kitchen is adorable w/ ceramic tiled flooring,  painted cabinetry, plenty of counter space and room for a gathering table. A little nature behind you w/ trees and a covered porch. There is an attached shed and pull down attic space as well as a crawl space for ample storage!! HOA fee covers roof, lawn maintenance and snow removal. Covered porch could be screened in . Washer and Dryer, Refrigerator, dishwasher, range, microwave  all convey in the sale in "AS IS " condition.  OWNER OCCUPANTS ONLY!!!!
